name: Anti-Aging Cream 1.7oz
description: The anti-aging cream is ideal for achieving smooth, luminous skin. Dark circles, puffiness, wrinkles, and uneven skin texture are targeted by its special combination of banana extract, retinol, and hyaluronic acid. All skin types can benefit; use morning and night for optimal results. Use this potent cream to fight those bothersome under-eye bags! Ingredients: Water (Aqua), Musa Sapientum (Banana) Fruit Extract, Polysorbate 20, Sodium Hyaluronate, Hydrolyzed Collagen, Retinol (and) Glycine Soja (Soybean) Oil, Bisabolol, Lavendula Official Oil, Vitamin E Acetate
